    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cook big burgers!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/bb851ef40858b30db09ea3f49b80b2c1.poster.avif?t=1753476831\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/bb851ef40858b30db09ea3f49b80b2c1.webm?t=1753476831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/bb851ef40858b30db09ea3f49b80b2c1.mp4?t=1753476831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push giant pieces of food into the correct order requested by customers. Rank up and upgrade your work station along the way to become a master chef!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interact with the people in town!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/0b651be4c9be665111c36e6650eb27db.poster.avif?t=1753476831\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/0b651be4c9be665111c36e6650eb27db.webm?t=1753476831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/0b651be4c9be665111c36e6650eb27db.mp4?t=1753476831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decide whether or not to interact with the unfolding story set inside the town. Completing quests or simply talking with strangers may prove to be beneficial.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive and participate in combat!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/61bf36f6199880d42bd45d3d828a42c2.poster.avif?t=1753476831\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/61bf36f6199880d42bd45d3d828a42c2.webm?t=1753476831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/61bf36f6199880d42bd45d3d828a42c2.mp4?t=1753476831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Load up with tools and a weapon by supporting one of the local shops. Defend against what lurks in the darkness and stay rich in health to uncover hidden secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore fun pastimes!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/e8f49e6c86f561f668597a84e69dde33.poster.avif?t=1753476831\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/e8f49e6c86f561f668597a84e69dde33.webm?t=1753476831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306170/extras/e8f49e6c86f561f668597a84e69dde33.mp4?t=1753476831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Catch fish and cook it by the furnace or maybe pass time playing video games at the arcade! And if the outside sounds like more fun, then enjoy competing in sports and racing events. Don't forget to test your luck at the casino!</p>",
